    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban restrictive covenants and make these unenforceable",
        "additional_details": "COVID19 pandemic and economic crisis has and is still affecting thousands of jobs across the UK. \r\n\r\nCompanies enforcing Restrictive Covenant into employees' contracts whilst laying personnel off could have a huge impact on people's professional lives, being hard enough to find new work as is. \r\n\r\nAnnulling imposed Restrictive Covenants would facilitate redundant professionals finding work.",
        "background": "Asking Parliament/Government to void all types of Restrictive Covenants by Law.",
